import { ArrowBackIosNew, Edit } from "@mui/icons-material"; import { Button, Container, Divider, Grid, IconButton, Typography, } from "@mui/material"; import { Box } from "@mui/system"; import MUIRichTextEditor from "mui-rte"; import React from "react"; import { useSelector } from "react-redux"; import { useHistory } from "react-router-dom"; const RSPHCMB = () => { const { data } = useSelector((state) => state.rsphcmb); const history = useHistory(); return (


WHO WE ARE

CONTENT history.push({ pathname: "/dashboard/about/rsphcmb/who_we_are_content", state: { content: data?.who_we_are, }, }) } >


VISION & MISSION STATEMENT history.push({ pathname: "/dashboard/about/rsphcmb/vision_mission_edit", state: { vision: data?.vision, mission: data?.mission, image: data?.visionImage, }, }) } >
VISION STATEMENT {data?.vision}
MISSION STATEMENT {data?.mission}


GOVERNOR history.push({ pathname: "/dashboard/about/rsphcmb/governor_edit", state: { governorName: data?.governorName, governorImage: data?.governorImage, deputyGovName: data?.deputyGovName, deputyGovImage: data?.deputyGovImage, }, }) } >
GOVERNOR {data?.vision}
MISSION STATEMENT {data?.mission}
); }; export default RSPHCMB;
